- I said I want the truth!

00:06:28.687 --> 00:06:33.457 align:middle line:10%
- She's my sister
and my daughter!

00:06:33.457 --> 00:06:38.440 align:middle line:10%
[CRYING] Khan, please, go back.

00:06:38.440 --> 00:06:40.400 align:middle line:10%
For God's sake, keep
her upstairs, go back.

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:48.370 align:middle line:90%


00:06:48.370 --> 00:06:56.292 align:middle line:10%
My father and I understand.

00:06:56.292 --> 00:06:57.555 align:middle line:10%
